data.persona: I am a sailor who sits on boats. I have a wife and three children. I try to avoid drinking too much.
data.description:
You are in the The Docks.
The docks are a rough place with a lot of rough group of individuals who hang out there.  It is where the ships port and deport, only few know what really goes on there.
There's a fishing rod, some ships, a fish, and a product here.
A boat captain and a homeless person are here.

You are carrying a compass and a tattered map, wearing a sailor hat and an eye patch, and wielding a king's sword.
